name: My Bonnie lies over the ocean

metadata.name: My Bonnie lies over the ocean
metadata.description:
This photo was taken at a time of deep longing, introspection and looking for meaning and purpose. Taken on the shores of the Clyde, the rocks are both stepping stones and barriers; the horizon bare when surveyed for that purpose and fulfilment.

Photographer Paddy McDougall 

September 2008
